parts.text:
```json
{
  "application": "Slurm",
  "details": {
    "description": "The script is a Slurm script designed to run a Python evaluation script using the 'machetli' library.",
    "resource_requirements": {
      "memory": "mem-per-cpu: {memory_per_cpu}",
      "partition": "{partition}",
      "qos": "{qos}",
      "tasks": "array=0-{num_tasks}",
      "priority": "nice={nice}",
      "mail": "mail-type={mailtype}, mail-user={mailuser}"
    },
    "environment": "environment_setup: {environment_setup}",
    "python_version": "python: {python}",
    "evaluation_script": "machetli.evaluator: {evaluator_path}",
    "state_file": "state_filename: {state_filename}",
    "run_directories": "run_dirs: {run_dirs}",
    "output_files": "driver.log, driver.err, exit_code",
    "extra_options": "extra_options: {extra_options}"
  }
}
```
